description: Weight distribution of (48,2^24,12) binary code obtained from Golay code of length 24 lifted to Z/4Z and mapped to GF(2)^2.
references: K. Tanabe, A criterion for designs in Z_4-codes on the symmetrized weight enumerator, Des. Codes Cryptogr. 30 (2003), 169-185.

A. Bonnecaze, P. Sole and A. R. Calderbank, Quaternary quadratic residue codes and unimodular lattices, IEEE Trans. Inform. Theory, Vol. 41, pages 366-377, 1995.
